# evolve owns the generated evaluation reports and results files — their
# output is deterministic, so reformatting would fight the tool.
EVALUATION.md
EVALUATION.json
plugins/*/EVALUATION.md
plugins/*/evals/*/results.json

# Prettier folds long frontmatter scalars onto multiple lines, but the skill
# `description` must stay single-line: it is the only activation signal and
# some harnesses parse frontmatter line-by-line. markdownlint still lints
# skill bodies (make lint).
plugins/*/skills/*/SKILL.md

# Local agent state (plans, settings) — not part of the published repo.
.claude/
